---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Solusi">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<header class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-8 overflow-hidden bg-grid">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-secondary-container/30 border border-outline-variant/15 rounded-full text-primary-fixed-dim text-xs font-label tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed-dim animate-pulse"></span>
Vector Integration Tech
</div>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tighter md: font-headline mb-8 max-w-4xl text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                ARSITEKTUR CERDAS UNTUK <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-fixed-dim to-on-primary-container">PERUSAHAAN MODERN.</span>
            </h1>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-10">
                Menyinkronkan aliran data tingkat tinggi dengan otomatisasi nalar untuk menciptakan efisiensi terdepan. Solusi bersistem presisi untuk ekosistem operasional yang kompleks.
            </p>
</div>
<!-- Abstract Decoration -->
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="abstract digital blue neural network nodes and data streams against a dark background with cinematic lighting and depth of field" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDlUEf8AazoSXePQr-1sFy6bFYajjVk6w-2In8MzuSdUWyS2-JBu5bJJ7fcA7MURNdN3X5pUZO1E2lA00vShiWK_2JPEvgH6obQ1wrYFNBlvh5fySLExV-HYZeV4V3X7xApDi6fMI6crwkCmGEIr0vsyZPRIA0Gd8tra5TmfsVMLIjZR8cWeImCmymJX0M8d0gls8U7OW6HlNhfkbN-jBbd2wzMtxP3oty_8YSvrmj2x-5o4bNobbSlYisbNUrxlft9mFSi5TQqzwdz"/>
</div>
</header>
<!-- Solutions Bento Grid -->
<section class="px-8 py-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6">
<!-- Enterprise Automation -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-10 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors duration-500 border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-6">settings_suggest</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-headline mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Otomatisasi Perusahaan</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-md">Hilangkan hambatan operasional dengan mesin alur kerja otonom yang beradaptasi dengan kecepatan bisnis Anda secara real-time.</p>
<ul class="space-y-3 mb-10 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg">check_circle</span>
                            Logika rantai pasokan optimalisasi mandiri
                        </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-medium">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-lg">check_circle</span>
                            Penjadwalan pemeliharaan prediktif
                        </li>
</ul>
<div class="mt-auto">
<button class="group/btn flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-fixed-dim font-bold font-headline uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">
                            Eksplorasi Otomatisasi
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-hover/btn:translate-x-1">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="close-up macro shot of computer microchips and circuits with cyan lighting and futuristic atmosphere" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDBVi0IGzITcDNtRRa8Lv9FjVRB49bN8VmWzZTRSO9Sk9j0gUOnGyRG1wGEtqe_LK1kNxnSZS5c-qf6-DBAxu1-0iutT3VomytxiGUQR9MdvXQK-2sNdTPS_DKYK7YtGgbw7mrywNu0KNQKNHBpBDzMbYMRtrdR282_idNRh5v5QC_SWIZNs-Zkcvt_4cle_f1jKfxyCktXq2L2xG5txmPRDxoycDXQ7OdwMHqc3vYzprrmCiO4Cex4_HazZv4GWvonKr10JkiyYptw"/>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Smart Business Systems -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-lg p-8 relative">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-3xl mb-4">hub</span>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Sistem Bisnis Cerdas</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">Kerangka komputasi terintegrasi yang menghubungkan data lama dengan sistem pendorong keputusan di masa depan.</p>
<div class="aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant/15">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60" data-alt="modern data visualization dashboard showing glowing blue graphs and metrics on a dark glass interface" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBfw5LX1JOa2loQzNy8cgF4p1Xae6GZZsRF70c7dZEXxYlPjaY7JCPS0VTELFMITDqmAaBLbfeSbeqWg91lWq9HlTomnpzkxICWGkFka3fTRYAyrJlZPiGF06FQNYlgwOQXcNhXWBdtYiOcglKfjmdEHzph9ZoMax7R6vVjMTJVP1s8OJMqScIZhCWFtIVIVSFX6jY-pvikZm3xSlrUZTFus0ZhY-smih_svfopya9db2DI4YBsROBBf_Wj111m7xhu8LY-C2GE1WYf"/>
</div>
<a class="inline-block w-full text-center py-3 border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 rounded-lg text-primary-fixed-dim font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-tighter hover:bg-primary-fixed-dim/10 transition-all" href="#">Minta Audit</a>
</div>
<!-- Data Intelligence -->
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl p-8 relative flex flex-col justify-between border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-3xl mb-4" data-weight="fill">insights</span>
<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-headline mb-3 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Kecerdasan Data</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm mb-6">Mengubah petabyte sinyal data mentah mendalam menjadi wawasan pasar yang presisi melalui analisis berbasis vektor.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-4 rounded-xl border-l-2 border-primary-fixed-dim border border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-outline mb-1 font-label">Siaran Waktu Nyata</div>
<div class="font-mono text-xs text-primary-fixed-dim">0x4F2... PROCESSING [98.2%]</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- AI Business Solutions -->
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-surface-container-low to-surface-container-lowest rounded-lg p-10 relative overflow-hidden group border border-outline-variant/10">
<div class="node-indicator"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-10 items-center">
<div class="flex-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim text-4xl mb-6">psychology</span>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold font-headline mb-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Solusi Bisnis AI</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant mb-6">Terapkan Model Bahasa Besar (LLM) khusus dan Agen AI Generatif yang dirancang khusus untuk vertikal data Anda.</p>
<button class="bg-primary-fixed-dim text-on-primary-fixed px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-black font-headline text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:brightness-110 transition-all">
                            Konsultasikan Strategi AI
                        </button>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full h-64 md:h-auto">
<img class="w-full h-full object-contain filter drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(76,214,255,0.3)]" data-alt="surreal digital 3D sculpture of a human head constructed from glowing crystalline nodes and fiber optics" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAMsM2UfcCEQiCU3y6MHDmDHW0cOjWraGcpKqpH-E7cSq1CFSFCDzeJ2o3T1AfmFs83dvdL0NgQPeza2gc2H0FIWspXyUC76yBTbVilOpgnJN_KuAb7nhU7DFsDBo2PnBWYG2TLnFyGMjUemCrj-n899GY7GE9_AIPpg1dXwO54RIjznSD4A1oHZ49a-Z6gpHL45DJwpIbDa3songQ1MSPuD_54QvyVvdZiminJQrcFkBFb-_UiLCf1yxyMgEN32OfWi5MWPE56-_az"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industry Metrics -->
<section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest border-y border-outline-variant/15">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 text-center">
<div>
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline text-primary-fixed-dim mb-2">40%</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline font-label">Peningkatan Efisiensi</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline text-primary-fixed-dim mb-2">2.4s</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline font-label">Latensi Rata-Rata</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline text-primary-fixed-dim mb-2">120+</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline font-label">Klien Global</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black font-headline text-primary-fixed-dim mb-2">99.9%</div>
<div class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-outline font-label">SLA Waktu Aktif</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Global Reach Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
<div class="md:w-1/2">
<h2 class="text-5xl font-black font-headline tracking-tighter mb-6 leading-tight text-slate-900 dark:text-white">INTEGRASI GLOBAL.<br/>DOMINASI LOKAL.</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">Infrastruktur kami tersebar di berbagai benua, memastikan bahwa agen cerdas dan alur kerja otomatis Anda selalu terhubung dengan pusat komersial global.</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
<div class="bg-surface-container-high px-4 py-2 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest font-label uppercase">US-EAST-1</span>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-high px-4 py-2 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest font-label uppercase">EU-WEST-2</span>
</div>
<div class="bg-surface-container-high px-4 py-2 rounded flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-fixed-dim"></span>
<span class="text-xs font-bold tracking-widest font-label uppercase">ASIA-PACIFIC</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:w-1/2 w-full aspect-video bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl overflow-hidden relative group border border-outline-variant/15">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-1000" data-alt="earth from space at night with glowing blue connection lines between major cities representing global data network" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC-aSKCcvDg9o_QpZA3pDEY363gYOan5VdQPQUF277j1C_U6BLcKXSBbTNmDHPM5yBB0KTRH70Vwt9ifr4eooiJOWd-7B5g7WcE0N59M_ouLHdg-Bl7qxjD1gdXPRLNwBMspIQaU1IXTgBnCbxHOA5pkxXHeey_RAulAbdA65ADWdwuafWVITMPW4is7Ce98ZFcGSbxHr2t4m-yxWyn1Xhj3epRCt7LVZpFRsw9xTkXYaHDqfYm_yEyoKN8Znd-YtpnjunIgryLsaDs"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background/80 to-transparent"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 flex items-center gap-2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary-fixed-dim">location_on</span>
<span class="font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-900 dark:text-white" data-location="Global">Pusat Jaringan</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-24 px-8">
<div class="glass-panel max-w-5xl mx-auto p-12 md:p-20 rounded-lg border border-outline-variant/10 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-fixed-dim/5 blur-[120px]"></div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-on-primary-container/10 blur-[120px]"></div>
<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black font-headline mb-8 tracking-tighter text-slate-900 dark:text-white">SIAP MERANCANG<br/>MASA DEPAN ANDA?</h2>
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
<button class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-fixed-dim to-on-primary-container text-on-primary-fixed px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold font-headline shadow-lg shadow-primary-fixed-dim/40 dark:shadow-primary-fixed-dim/20 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:brightness-110 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group w-full md:w-auto">
                    Jadwalkan Sesi Strategi
                </button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-highest/50 border border-primary-fixed-dim/20 text-on-surface px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-black font-headline text-base uppercase tracking-[0.1em] transition-all hover:bg-surface-container-highest">
                    Unduh Buku Putih
                </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>

<style>
.glass-panel {
    background: rgba(16, 20, 26, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
}
.bg-grid {
    background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(76, 214, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(76, 214, 255, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 40px 40px;
}
</style>
</BaseLayout>
